locality: Along National Road 25 7 - 15 km W of Ranomafana between the towns of Ambodiamontana and Vohiparara. Secondary vegetation deriving from moist montane forest transitioning to sclerophyllous montane forest at higher elevations characterized by trees of Weinmannia spp., MONIMIACEAE (Tambourissa, Decarydendron, Ephippiandra), LAURACEAE (primarily Ocotea and Cryptocarya) and understory with abundant Psychotria spp. and Oncostemum spp.
Eastern Domain: 22 km. N. of Ifarantsa and 33 km N. of Hwy 13 (Ambovombe-Tôlan|2aro (Fort Dauphin)) along road which passes along eastern boundary of Parcel 1 of Reserve #11 (Andohahela).
Est: Mont Vatovavy (entre Antsenavolo et Kianjavato), bassin de la Mananjary.
